<h1>Welcome to the Animal Preservation System</h1>
<h2>The Most Respected Animal Matchmaker for International Zoos</h2>
<p>The Animal Preservation System is committed to matching possible mates held
    in captivity for the preservation of their species. We keep a database of
    the anmials available so that you can pair up possible mates for at-risk
    animals in your home zoo.</p>


    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <h2>animals</h2>
            <div class="row">
                {{#each animals}}
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="card mb-3">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title"><a href="/{{this._zoo}}">{{this.scientificName}} {{this.commonName}}</a></h5>
                            <p class="card-text">{{this.email}}</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{/each}}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>